1213
01:35:30.856 --> 01:35:31.857
Alex.

1214
01:35:32.524 --> 01:35:33.567
Sit.

1215
01:35:39.364 --> 01:35:41.033
Don't worry about your parents.

1216
01:35:41.116 --> 01:35:42.409
